      <title>Nvidia 内部人士趁股价上涨获利，股票销售额突破 7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-nvda-insiders-cash-in-on-rally-as-share-sales-top-700-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场对英伟达芯片的需求持续旺盛，该公司股价不断攀升至历史最高水平，今年以来，该公司内部人士已出售了价值超过 7 亿美元的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-nvda-insiders-cash-in-on-rally-as-share-sales-top-700-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险买盘与疲软数据相互影响，美元未达 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/dollar-eyes-fresh-high-for-year-on-haven-bid-political-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管有证据表明美国经济正在放缓，但美元仍有望创下 2024 年新高，因为投资者寻求躲避欧洲政治不确定性，从而支撑了美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/dollar-eyes-fresh-high-for-year-on-haven-bid-political-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:40:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
